OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCovid mask rules relaxed   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor EU air travel          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Face masks will no longer have to be   
OL,6, worn on flights and in airports in EU  
OL,7, countries from next Monday, according  
OL,8, to new official guidance.              
OL,10,FThe move is in line with changing Covid
OL,11,Fpolicies on public transport across    
OL,12,FEurope, said the EU Aviation Safety    
OL,13,FAgency (EASA).                         
OL,15,FSome US airlines did the same in April 
OL,16,Fafter a federal judge threw out the    
OL,17,Fgovernment's mask mandate.             
OL,19,FBut EASA said rules for masks "will    
OL,20,Fcontinue to vary by airline".          
